<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Registration Successful</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-container {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      h1 {
        color: #333;
      }

      p {
        color: #555;
      }

      .success-message {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #4caf50;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <h1>Congratulations, <%= fullName %>!</h1>
      <p>Your registration with our RA.one Shop was successful.</p>

      <p>
        Thank you for joining us. We look forward to providing you with a great
        shopping experience.
      </p>

      <div class="success-message">Let's practice together!</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
